{"tid":498584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[呢獲撐白鴿] 胡志偉提「狡兔死走狗烹」　謝偉俊投訴侮辱：咩叫走狗？　梁君彥要求收回","createTime":"2017-12-14T02:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T16:43:52.000Z","uid":23707,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f25b60b049486fc002f3372b45dfab45b66574","tid":498584,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:42:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513216216332\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513216216332&d=yokb69uU2TaPlFT3jV6eCwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=33769859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513216216332&h=96877870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513216216332</a>"},{"pid":"0904427c8b9052aa8210620e9123ca353413d7f1","tid":498584,"uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:43:08.000Z","msg":"民主黨胡志偉發言時表示，若修改了《議事規則》，將會「一路沿用，是永續情況」，直指「今日你好好彩，好似（建制派議員）謝偉俊，自認係西環契仔，今日你就企喺建制派保皇黨嗰一邊，但係你聽日用完咗個價值&hellip;&hellip;中國有句名言，『狡兔死，走狗烹』，謝偉俊你作為『走狗』嘅一部分，點可能唔係會將來受到中央政府唾棄呢？」<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊隨即投訴胡志偉言論冒犯，「我可以忍一次，可以忍兩次，我唔可以忍第三次！咩叫『走狗』啊？」他指，若胡志偉無法解釋何謂「走狗」，就是侮辱，應該收回言論及道歉，「作為一黨主席，唔該你道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉重申他只是引用中國「狡兔死，走狗烹」說法，「我只係講你係『走狗』嘅一部分&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 這時大會主席梁君彥表示，「我係好清楚你係指謝偉俊，我希望你收返對謝偉俊嘅言論，等辯論可以繼續」。<br />\n<br />\n不過胡志偉指，不認為其言論冒犯，「你要對號入座嘅話&hellip;&hellip;」現場建制派接着起哄。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥於是暫停會議處理裁決。會議再開後，胡志偉承認其言論後期只針對謝偉俊並不適當，決定收回「對謝偉俊」部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d9b75a046d1773307c1cccbd87524f843298f9e0","tid":498584,"uid":61105,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"咁又拖左d時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b3627bcea225e130792035f25dba34c883e526","tid":498584,"uid":47359,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:46:51.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n敢做唔敢認<br />\n廢鳩<br />\n而家奶共好失禮咩？"},{"pid":"261d8fb63b6fd71b9f670c8158d264ccf3856a39","tid":498584,"uid":116289,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:47:24.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89846bb41e5af5ad28f60dc5f56c3f743d3f486c","tid":498584,"uid":11840,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民主黨胡志偉發言時表示，若修改了《議事規則》，將會「一路沿用，是永續情況」，直指「今日你好好彩，好似（建制派議員）謝偉俊，自認係西環契仔，今日你就企喺建制派保皇黨嗰一邊，但係你聽日用完咗個價值&hellip;&hellip;中國有句名言，『狡兔死，走狗烹』，謝偉俊你作為『走狗』嘅一部分，點可能唔係會將來受到中央政府唾棄呢？」<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊隨即投訴胡志偉言論冒犯，「我可以忍一次，可以忍兩次，我唔可以忍第三次！咩叫『走狗』啊？」他指，若胡志偉無法解釋何謂「走狗」，就是侮辱，應該收回言論及道歉，「作為一黨主席，唔該你道歉」。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉重申他只是引用中國「狡兔死，走狗烹」說法，「我只係講你係『走狗』嘅一部分&hellip;&hellip;」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 這時大會主席梁君彥表示，「我係好清楚你係指謝偉俊，我希望你收返對謝偉俊嘅言論，等辯論可以繼續」。<br />\n<br />\n不過胡志偉指，不認為其言論冒犯，「你要對號入座嘅話&hellip;&hellip;」現場建制派接着起哄。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥於是暫停會議處理裁決。會議再開後，胡志偉承認其言論後期只針對謝偉俊並不適當，決定收回「對謝偉俊」部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n決定收回「對謝偉俊」部分<br />\n即係斷水流大師兄<br />\n在座各位都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd61dc3c8398ba43e64fe89b23de28bee247d70","tid":498584,"uid":10453,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"收回言論，謝偉俊唔係走狗，係狡兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6527f7601e9bfc3406210ce801439964cd8b8e60","tid":498584,"uid":61280,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:50:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兩邊共狗都幾撚好交流，不愧練慣戲！！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a22ab5482e457fd5638db8f8e06fe812263792","tid":498584,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:55:26.000Z","msg":"原文係咁，中性字來，關侮辱乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac078b0f04b89e5381a26bbf756647a07bd6108f","tid":498584,"uid":13115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:55:48.000Z","msg":"走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d44021f841bdeee9249c89987b56e56c4dccce","tid":498584,"uid":38316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"撚狗拖時間呢招掂"},{"pid":"c427e424f3ef6fd9befa83ff5ce9048e8c80c61b","tid":498584,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb1f3f6084e1bd94be23eca4ba8653b0c00e7c9","tid":498584,"uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撚狗拖時間呢招掂</blockquote><br />\n睇下邊條柒頭抵唔到頸"},{"pid":"fa0911427c7950d85bad14137fd0edadb71fd8e7","tid":498584,"uid":121473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"呢d中國典故野要睇毓民先精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048a6adeb18d73dab136dc6fb902ddda9385b96c","tid":498584,"uid":93784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"走狗有幾難明?<br />\n做共產黨條走狗 預左用完即棄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa